data.description: Don't miss this beautiful home that features 4 bedrooms with the primary bedroom downstairs, 2.5 bathrooms a large island kitchen, upstairs family room and a dedicated dining room/office area just off the main entry. Enjoy the wonderful natural light from the large windows and high ceilings. Convenient access to Loop 1604/I-10/I-35, Randolph AFB and Ft Sam, the Forum, and IKEA. Walking distance to neighborhood park.
